{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420061259","title":"Arsitektur nyata adalah shared understanding expert developer","desc":"Fowler: setelah diskusi dengan Ralph Johnson, arsitektur lebih tepat dipahami sebagai pemahaman kolektif tentang desain sistem daripada label 'fundamental'.","tags":["permanent-note","software-architecture","architecture","martin-fowler"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"cbec6b0859bb26c38c963561a6ab68b3","updated":1776683200322,"created":1776683200322,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.software-architecture","alias":"software-architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.software-architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.martin-fowler","alias":"martin-fowler","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.martin-fowler"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":937},"end":{"line":20,"column":52,"offset":986},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420061232","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1037},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1062},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061232"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420060928","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1119},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1144},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":3,"offset":2345},"end":{"line":35,"column":28,"offset":2370},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420061259"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061356","id":"zettel.20260420061356","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1264},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1289},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420061259"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062009","id":"zettel.20260420062009","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":1065},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":1090},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420061259"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":3,"offset":2510},"end":{"line":42,"column":28,"offset":2535},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420061259"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"arsitektur-nyata-adalah-shared-understanding-expert-developer\">Arsitektur nyata adalah shared understanding expert developer<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#arsitektur-nyata-adalah-shared-understanding-expert-developer\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"A better view of architecture was the shared understanding that the expert developers have of the system design.\"</p>\n<p>Sumber: <a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/architecture/\">https://martinfowler.com/architecture/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fowler mengutip diskusi dengan Ralph Johnson untuk menantang definisi arsitektur yang berbasis \"fundamental\" atau \"high level\".</li>\n<li>Johnson menunjukkan bahwa tidak ada cara objektif untuk menentukan apa yang benar-benar fundamental.</li>\n<li>Sebagai gantinya, arsitektur lebih relevan bila dipahami sebagai shared understanding yang hidup di antara expert developer.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Jika tim inti memahami batasan sistem, alasan desain, dan titik rawan, itu lebih dekat ke arsitektur nyata daripada seratus diagram yang tidak dipakai.</li>\n<li>Arsitektur menjadi fenomena kolektif, bukan artefak statis yang bisa dipatok dari luar.</li>\n<li>Praktik arsitektural yang efektif membutuhkan komunikasi, pembelajaran bersama, dan pemahaman kontekstual di dalam tim.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a> — ringkasan halaman Software Architecture Guide</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061232\">Fowler memulai definisi arsitektur dengan kritik terhadap ‘fundamental organization’</a> — kritik terhadap definisi \"fundamental organization\"</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060928\">Arsitektur bukan kasta; dia harus hidup bersama kode</a> — arsitektur harus hidup bersama kode</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">martin-fowler (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061356\">Arsitektur bukan sekadar keputusan awal proyek</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420062009\">Architect bukan jabatan; dia adalah kemampuan judgment desain</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"seeds":{"dendron.templates":{}},"enableFullHierarchyNoteTitle":false},"preview":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTag